name: Asm
body:
# asm  

## Projects 
1. Sort numbers  
2. Sort structures  
3. Check if prime  
4. Range  

## Guide
### Asm Vim -> Run  
```
vim main.s; gcc -c main.s -o obj; gcc obj -o bin; ./bin
```

### C Vim -> Asm Vim  
```
vim main.c; gcc -c -S -O3 main.c; vim main.s
```
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
